Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:13.63,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The mysterious figure making a\Nstir at Kanyasai: Phantom Thief Jumoji
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.05,0:00:19.60,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Global Act Club
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.39,0:01:13.00,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You hold your breath to make it through\Nthe bewildering day that confronts you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:19.17,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what this is, don't you?\NWhat do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:25.76,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain from shrugging\Nit all off as nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.79,0:01:31.68,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,urges you on enough to be encouraging
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.71,0:01:38.23,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Catching hold but making a mess,\Nwe're still inadequate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:46.26,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but as long as we can forge\Nour shining, unseen future selves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:54.70,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Awaken and run where it takes you,\Nleaving mirages behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:02:01.25,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Run with your desire to change,\Nfrom your comfort zone into freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:08.68,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Start choosing between now\Nand the brilliance you can attain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:16.71,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Unaware of your destination,\Ndeep breaths following shallow ones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:27.10,SignsT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(521,283)}The Final Target
