Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.06,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,271)}Hyouka \NWhen light findeth equal measure \Nwith darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:15.58,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,54th Kanyasai
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:31.41,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Science Prep Room
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.11,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kugayama Muneyoshi\N(Student Council President)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.57,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"lost"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.98,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"Christie's ultra-famous work"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:30.78,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,On Air
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.37,0:24:26.37,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,This situation is an unscientific\Nmontage of emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:29.64,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is calling whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.67,0:24:35.57,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Your gaze darts away when I turn around\N(I can feel it)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.60,0:24:37.86,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unkind to tell me I'm imagining things
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.89,0:24:43.37,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say having\Nantennas is a talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.40,0:24:48.45,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean I want to know\N(I mean) (don't you?)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.48,0:24:55.25,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn up the heat on your youth\Nfor you now, while there's time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:59.92,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can solve this tomorrow,\Nwhy not solve it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.95,0:25:05.51,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to solve your mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.54,0:25:10.23,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Track down that secretive boyish figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.26,0:25:17.82,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Today) you are a fantasy,\Ndrawing me to you, no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.85,0:25:23.36,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My curiosity is expanding,\Nlack of tricks notwithstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.39,0:25:30.36,Top Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fascinated, and I have to know, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.28,0:25:41.04,SignsT,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,208)}The Kudryavka Sequence
